As we nurse the wounds of 2020, let’s pray that 2021 will treat us kindly. That it will look at our faces and sympathise with our long trek to safety and wipe away our tears of despondency. 
Have a blessed New Year.
Mr Onyango is a high school teacher. jamesonyango26@gmail.com. In his new year’s message to the country, the President called for a renewal of minds in the New Year 2021. He paraded the newly elected Msambweni MP Feisal Bader as the “firstborn” of the so called Hustler's Movement. Ever since Abiy Ahmed came to power, the Tigray regional government has been at odds with the central government.